snippet.title: Groove Gunner Early Access Trailer
snippet.description: Groove Gunner is a VR rhythm game where you switch between shooting and blocking approaching targets and bullets.  With a variety of musical genres, each song features hand crafted sequences, matching light shows, and multiple difficulty levels.
